UML:TaggedValue.value: Informal caregiver (for example relative of AP) registers uStore and defines his role and connection to AP. uStore asks for permission from AP to add this person as his caregiver and to allow him to see/use part of his personal information. After confirmation, the caregiver can login to uStore and search based on platform and specific needs of the AP. Finally caregiver finds some appropriate service for AP and offers it to AP through uStore. AP can select to order it or to ignore the offer.
